VNC安装CentOS7.8: virt-install --name centos78 --virt-type kvm --os-type linux --os-variant rhel7 --memory 2048 --vcpus 2 --disk path=/data/images/centos7.qcow2,format=qcow2,size=10,bus=virtio --cdrom /data/iso/CentOS-7-x86_64-Minimal-2009.iso --graphics vnc,listen=0.0.0.0,port=5911 --network bridge=br0,model=virtio --noautoconsole
VNC安装windows: virt-install --name win2k16 --virt-type kvm --os-type windows --os-variant win2k16 --memory 2048 --vcpus 2 --network bridge=br0,model=virtio --disk path=/usr/share/virtio-win/virtio-win-0.1.171_amd64.vfd,device=floppy --cdrom /data/iso/cn_windows_server_2016_x64_dvd_9718765.iso --disk path=/data/images/win2k16.qcow2,bus=virtio,size=20,format=qcow2 --graphics vnc,listen=0.0.0.0,port=5910 --noautoconsole
